    <worksheet margin="1in" bottom="1.25cm" xml:id="Week1">
            <title>Math 121 Week 1 Activity</title>

        <objectives>
		<p>
            In this activity we will do the following:
        </p>
        <ul>
	  		<li>
	  			<p>
					Review the basic forms of linear, quadratic, and exponential functions.
	  			</p>
	  		</li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Identify functions of each of the above types from their graphs.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Find formulas for functions in the families given above from points on their graphs.
                </p>
            </li>
	  	</ul>
    </objectives>
            <introduction>
                <p>
                    This activity is intended to help you review some of the algebraic functions you saw in previous math courses. Please feel free to work together. If you get stuck, just ask and we'll get unstuck.
                </p>
            </introduction>
        <page>
            <exercise>
                <introduction>
                    <p>
